Data Copyright and Use Restrictions
===================================

The datasets, maps, figures, and derived products displayed or referenced 
in this repository remain the intellectual property of the 
**Berambadi Watershed Research Program**, Department of Civil Engineering, 
**Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bengaluru**, and its collaborators.

These data are provided in **aggregated, non-identifiable** form only 
for demonstration and educational purposes. They may not be copied, 
redistributed, or used for independent analysis or publication without 
explicit permission.

For research use or collaboration regarding Berambadi watershed data, 
please contact:

**Prof. Sekhar Muddu**  
Principal Investigator, REWARD Project  
Department of Civil Engineering, IISc Bengaluru  
Email: sekhar.muddu@gmail.com  

